WEBVTT

01:37.820 --> 01:40.580
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.320 --> 01:43.600
[Episode 24]

01:46.509 --> 01:48.240
Sister-in-law, you're awake.

01:48.759 --> 01:49.759
Who are you?

01:50.710 --> 01:51.840
Just call me Xiao Sha.

01:51.840 --> 01:52.700
This is my home.

01:53.120 --> 01:54.280
You were injured that day.

01:54.280 --> 01:55.410
Lu brought you back.

01:55.840 --> 01:56.640
I see.

01:56.870 --> 01:57.479
Thank you.

01:57.509 --> 01:58.200
You're welcome.

01:58.200 --> 01:59.840
Lu and I are like real brothers.

01:59.840 --> 02:01.200
His business is my business.

02:01.200 --> 02:02.590
His enemies are my enemies.

02:02.590 --> 02:03.720
As for his family...

02:07.070 --> 02:08.669
I must take good care of them.

02:09.120 --> 02:09.840
Where is he?

02:10.310 --> 02:11.970
Lu went out to buy some things.

02:12.240 --> 02:13.190
He's been gone for a while.

02:13.190 --> 02:15.120
I guess he should be back soon.

02:15.280 --> 02:15.910
Sister-in-law,

02:15.910 --> 02:17.120
please sit and have some tea

02:17.120 --> 02:18.240
while waiting for him.

02:18.240 --> 02:18.870
Okay.

02:24.430 --> 02:26.310
Are you also a cultivator?

02:26.530 --> 02:28.260
I am a disciple of Xin Xie Manor.

02:29.150 --> 02:29.950
Xin Xie Manor?

02:30.430 --> 02:31.120
I know.

02:31.190 --> 02:32.390
You guys are amazing.

02:33.400 --> 02:34.790
Are you a local?

02:35.120 --> 02:35.630
Yes.

02:36.400 --> 02:38.690
My family has lived here for generations.

02:38.690 --> 02:40.120
Then how did you and Lu Qianqiao

02:40.120 --> 02:41.000
meet?

02:42.170 --> 02:43.400
It's a long story.

02:43.630 --> 02:45.470
I was young and ignorant.

02:45.640 --> 02:46.250
Once,

02:46.280 --> 02:47.430
I offended Lu.

02:47.630 --> 02:49.160
He taught me a harsh lesson.

02:50.190 --> 02:52.190
After that, I was forced onto
the right path.

02:52.190 --> 02:52.910
Forced?

02:53.400 --> 02:53.910
Yes.

02:54.120 --> 02:55.579
At first, I was reluctant.

02:55.750 --> 02:57.360
But then I gradually realized

02:57.360 --> 02:58.079
that my former buddies

02:58.079 --> 02:59.440
who fooled around

02:59.470 --> 03:00.190
all didn't end up well.

03:00.190 --> 03:01.450
Then it all made sense.

03:01.520 --> 03:02.400
Lu

03:02.470 --> 03:03.500
looks cold but has a warm heart.

03:03.500 --> 03:04.940
He always takes good care

03:05.280 --> 03:06.680
of anyone he cares about.

03:07.470 --> 03:09.270
He is indeed that kind of person.

03:10.470 --> 03:11.600
So, Sister-in-law,

03:11.680 --> 03:12.840
how did you and Lu

03:13.190 --> 03:14.360
meet?

03:15.520 --> 03:18.310
We met through marriage.

03:19.800 --> 03:21.010
You're already married?

03:21.010 --> 03:22.570
Lu moves fast, doesn't he?

03:22.800 --> 03:23.680
So, Sister-in-law,

03:23.680 --> 03:25.000
where are you settling down now?

03:25.000 --> 03:26.470
If I go to the Central Plains
in the future,

03:26.470 --> 03:27.680
I can visit you.

03:28.079 --> 03:29.079
Settling down?

03:29.310 --> 03:30.640
We haven't decided yet.

03:31.560 --> 03:32.630
Haven't decided?

03:33.520 --> 03:35.850
We got separated right after our wedding.

03:36.310 --> 03:37.840
A lot happened afterwards,

03:38.220 --> 03:40.150
and we just arrived in North Xiang.

03:40.240 --> 03:42.120
So as for our future plans,

03:42.240 --> 03:43.570
we haven't decided yet.

03:44.190 --> 03:45.280
Well then, Sister-in-law,

03:45.280 --> 03:46.280
where do you like?

03:46.720 --> 03:48.490
Do you want to stay in North Xiang?

03:48.490 --> 03:49.400
Why not stay in Phoenix City

03:49.400 --> 03:50.190
and become my neighbor?

03:50.190 --> 03:51.340
Better not.

03:52.030 --> 03:53.800
I have to return to Xin Xie Manor.

03:53.800 --> 03:55.800
My Master and juniors are all there.

03:56.240 --> 03:57.610
Besides, I'm not used to the weather

03:57.610 --> 03:58.430
in North Xiang.

03:58.430 --> 03:59.310
It's too dry.

03:59.560 --> 04:00.290
That's true.

04:00.400 --> 04:02.120
You still have the immortal sect.

04:02.120 --> 04:03.000
Unlike Lu,

04:03.030 --> 04:03.630
who only needs to

04:03.630 --> 04:04.830
worry about himself.

04:20.920 --> 04:22.560
Your body hasn't recovered yet.

04:22.560 --> 04:24.270
It's best not to appear in public
for the time being.

04:24.270 --> 04:25.070
We also shouldn’t take anything

04:25.070 --> 04:26.000
from the inn.

04:26.430 --> 04:27.270
I bought you some

04:27.270 --> 04:28.600
clothes to change into,

04:28.750 --> 04:29.800
delicious pastries,

04:29.800 --> 04:30.720
and some folktales

04:30.720 --> 04:31.450
to kill time.

04:38.560 --> 04:39.159
Come.

04:39.720 --> 04:40.390
Try them on.

04:55.630 --> 04:56.430
Do they fit?

04:56.600 --> 04:57.730
They fit perfectly.

04:59.560 --> 05:00.600
I don't know how to cook,

05:00.600 --> 05:02.390
and Sha's cooking isn't good either.

05:02.390 --> 05:03.190
I just ordered some dishes

05:03.190 --> 05:04.250
at the restaurant.

05:04.390 --> 05:05.920
The waiter will deliver them in a while.

05:05.920 --> 05:07.120
If you're hungry,

05:07.430 --> 05:08.630
you can eat some pastries first

05:08.630 --> 05:09.830
to fill your stomach.

05:10.310 --> 05:11.270
That's great.

05:17.560 --> 05:18.830
Did you hear

05:19.240 --> 05:20.570
everything I just said?

05:22.070 --> 05:23.390
You knew I was outside?

05:24.000 --> 05:25.530
I'm a cultivator after all.

05:25.860 --> 05:26.990
You stood there for so long.

05:26.990 --> 05:28.390
I didn't notice at first,

05:28.390 --> 05:29.800
but I definitely realised later.

05:29.800 --> 05:31.190
So you said all that

05:31.480 --> 05:33.140
intentionally for me to hear?

05:33.620 --> 05:34.570
Of course not.

05:35.190 --> 05:37.430
But it's fine if you heard it.

05:39.720 --> 05:41.250
You don't like North Xiang.

05:43.120 --> 05:43.920
Not exactly.

05:45.020 --> 05:47.360
I just don't want to be too far
from my Master

05:47.360 --> 05:48.409
and my juniors.

05:48.820 --> 05:50.080
Especially my junior—

05:50.240 --> 05:51.840
she’s really attached to me.

05:52.720 --> 05:53.720
When I was in Chongling Valley,

05:53.720 --> 05:54.390
I saw her.

05:55.040 --> 05:55.900
She seemed like

05:56.260 --> 05:58.060
a very straightforward person.

05:58.480 --> 06:00.430
That's because you
don't know her well enough.

06:00.430 --> 06:01.830
My junior might look like

06:01.840 --> 06:03.640
a little leopard on the outside,

06:03.890 --> 06:05.590
but she's really just a little kitten.

06:05.590 --> 06:07.250
She's very delicate and cute.

06:07.670 --> 06:08.340
Really?

06:08.750 --> 06:09.360
Really.

06:09.510 --> 06:10.190
Believe me.

06:10.560 --> 06:12.310
Our Xin Xie Manor is very big,

06:12.760 --> 06:14.690
and only the three of us live there.

06:15.270 --> 06:16.000
Actually...

06:16.070 --> 06:16.750
Xin Mei.

06:17.720 --> 06:19.580
After I finish renewing my blood,

06:19.750 --> 06:22.080
my cultivation will drop significantly.

06:22.150 --> 06:23.420
It will be roughly equivalent to

06:23.420 --> 06:24.800
the Foundation Establishment Stage

06:24.800 --> 06:26.190
of you human cultivators.

06:26.190 --> 06:26.920
I know.

06:27.270 --> 06:30.000
I'm also at
the Foundation Establishment Stage.

06:30.680 --> 06:32.040
After renewing my blood,

06:32.040 --> 06:33.430
I also need to transform my heart.

06:33.430 --> 06:34.270
At that time,

06:34.430 --> 06:35.390
I will lose all of

06:35.390 --> 06:36.650
the War Demon's powers

06:37.070 --> 06:38.680
and become an ordinary person.

06:38.680 --> 06:40.190
You have to transform your heart?

06:40.190 --> 06:41.650
Will it be very dangerous?

06:43.310 --> 06:44.430
It's fine.

06:44.630 --> 06:45.490
I can handle it.

06:46.159 --> 06:47.000
But you can already

06:47.000 --> 06:48.159
feel the pain by now.

06:48.800 --> 06:49.870
Would transforming hearts

06:49.870 --> 06:51.310
hurt a lot?

06:53.390 --> 06:55.480
You still don't understand what I mean.

06:55.480 --> 06:56.510
I mean,

06:56.800 --> 06:57.530
afterwards,

06:57.630 --> 06:59.490
I will become an ordinary person.

07:00.040 --> 07:01.070
I will lose my power

07:01.070 --> 07:02.000
and magic.

07:02.390 --> 07:03.190
I'll no longer be able to

07:03.190 --> 07:05.360
help you with any difficulties
you may encounter

07:05.360 --> 07:06.820
in the Cultivation Realm.

07:08.310 --> 07:09.480
Then I just won't live

07:09.480 --> 07:10.940
in the Cultivation Realm.

07:15.600 --> 07:17.130
Let's go back to Wei County.

07:17.390 --> 07:18.520
That's my hometown.

07:18.990 --> 07:20.320
You've lived there too.

07:20.820 --> 07:21.520
And the Emperor

07:21.520 --> 07:22.630
has already publicly declared that

07:22.630 --> 07:24.160
your name has been cleared.

07:24.360 --> 07:25.490
You don't even know.

07:25.500 --> 07:26.450
The people there

07:26.480 --> 07:28.510
now revere you as a living saint

07:28.680 --> 07:30.270
and are building shrines
and temples for you.

07:30.270 --> 07:31.920
And there are Lu Xiaodao and Lu Jiujiu.

07:31.920 --> 07:33.270
They are your foster children.

07:33.270 --> 07:34.800
They are living a good life.

07:35.600 --> 07:37.720
If you are willing to go back
and live there,

07:37.720 --> 07:39.980
you will definitely live a good life too.

07:40.480 --> 07:41.560
Are you saying

07:42.040 --> 07:43.190
you're willing to become

07:43.190 --> 07:44.480
an ordinary person with me,

07:44.480 --> 07:46.540
and give up cultivating altogether?

07:47.000 --> 07:48.800
My Dao heart is unstable anyway.

07:49.040 --> 07:50.510
I probably won't achieve much

07:50.510 --> 07:52.190
on this path of cultivation.

07:53.040 --> 07:55.510
And when I went back to
Wei County previously,

07:55.510 --> 07:57.070
I saw my old friends.

07:57.510 --> 07:58.560
I thought then,

07:59.240 --> 08:00.970
if I hadn't left home back then,

08:01.560 --> 08:02.430
maybe,

08:03.630 --> 08:04.720
maybe I would have already lived

08:04.720 --> 08:06.310
an ordinary and happy life.

08:12.770 --> 08:15.370
♪ Once again I see
the world's cold indifference ♪

08:15.400 --> 08:18.390
♪ Bending what I've cherished
all my life ♪

08:17.070 --> 08:17.800
Xin Mei.

08:18.410 --> 08:23.760
♪ Illusions and vanity blind the eyes,
how could one still care ♪

08:18.600 --> 08:19.390
Thank you.

08:23.510 --> 08:24.360
Lu Qianqiao.

08:24.610 --> 08:27.270
♪ Having seen the widespread devastation ♪

08:24.750 --> 08:26.350
I have my conditions though.

08:27.120 --> 08:27.750
Tell me.

08:27.640 --> 08:30.450
♪ How could I look on and ignore it? ♪

08:29.120 --> 08:30.630
I want to bring my junior along.

08:30.630 --> 08:31.360
Sure.

08:30.930 --> 08:33.100
♪ If I do not fear the grave soil ♪

08:32.270 --> 08:33.200
I also want to go back often

08:33.130 --> 08:36.490
♪ I walk this path alone ♪

08:33.200 --> 08:34.130
to see my Master.

08:34.600 --> 08:35.480
Okay.

08:36.669 --> 08:39.650
♪ So that all may share in ♪

08:36.909 --> 08:38.200
And I want to live

08:38.200 --> 08:39.600
in my Auntie's old house.

08:39.669 --> 08:42.549
♪ The road to immortality ♪

08:39.840 --> 08:41.000
Because there are many

08:41.000 --> 08:42.570
of my friends and neighbors there.

08:42.570 --> 08:48.350
♪ I fear not defying
immortal laws and sacred precepts ♪

08:42.669 --> 08:43.360
It's very lively.

08:43.360 --> 08:44.200
No problem.

09:04.870 --> 09:06.360
A-Sheng, A-Sheng!

09:06.790 --> 09:08.480
Follow me, follow me!

09:13.790 --> 09:14.840
The head chef of Shanfu Vegetarian

09:14.840 --> 09:16.120
had retired and returned to his hometown.

09:16.120 --> 09:17.910
It's his apprentice cooking now,

09:17.910 --> 09:19.570
and the cooking is much worse.

09:19.790 --> 09:20.390
Here.

09:21.870 --> 09:22.550
Thank you.

09:24.510 --> 09:25.390
I say, Lu,

09:25.720 --> 09:27.390
you’ve already married my sister-in-law.

09:27.390 --> 09:28.920
Why are you still so polite?

09:29.270 --> 09:30.440
Just eat your food.

09:30.630 --> 09:31.890
Why do you talk so much?

09:34.120 --> 09:34.750
Sha.

09:35.150 --> 09:36.440
You are not young anymore.

09:36.440 --> 09:37.970
Why aren't you married yet?

09:38.390 --> 09:40.080
Love is a deadly poison.

09:40.420 --> 09:41.950
I'm doing quite well alone.

09:41.960 --> 09:42.860
Why should I find someone

09:42.860 --> 09:43.790
to control me?

09:44.320 --> 09:45.000
Besides,

09:45.030 --> 09:46.030
I have high standards.

09:46.030 --> 09:46.890
Ordinary girls

09:47.080 --> 09:48.140
don't catch my eye.

09:55.510 --> 09:56.150
Coming!

09:56.620 --> 09:57.530
Sister-in-law, Lu,

09:57.530 --> 09:58.330
you eat first.

10:11.870 --> 10:12.600
You...

10:13.840 --> 10:14.980
Is my senior here?

10:18.510 --> 10:19.270
Sheng!

10:21.200 --> 10:21.990
Senior!

10:36.530 --> 10:37.800
I finally found you.

10:55.660 --> 10:56.720
That day in Xutuo City,

10:56.720 --> 10:57.910
you left a letter and left

10:57.910 --> 10:59.570
without even saying goodbye.

10:59.600 --> 11:01.330
It doesn't look like you at all.

11:04.030 --> 11:04.600
Sheng?

11:06.320 --> 11:06.910
Sheng?

11:11.780 --> 11:12.580
You're hurt.

11:13.120 --> 11:13.860
No.

11:14.320 --> 11:15.080
Let me see.

11:15.600 --> 11:16.460
I'm really not.

11:17.120 --> 11:18.630
Senior, I'm fine.

11:23.900 --> 11:25.120
It just looks scary.

11:25.200 --> 11:26.670
The wound is actually very small.

11:26.670 --> 11:27.870
Don't worry about it.

11:28.200 --> 11:29.730
Are you hurt anywhere else?

11:30.090 --> 11:30.610
No.

11:34.360 --> 11:34.890
Brother.

11:35.270 --> 11:36.080
That's...

11:36.360 --> 11:37.790
Sister-in-law's junior?

11:37.790 --> 11:38.790
Her name is Sheng?

11:58.510 --> 11:59.080
Senior,

11:59.820 --> 12:00.790
don't be sad.

12:01.370 --> 12:02.770
It doesn't hurt anymore.

12:03.480 --> 12:04.600
Who hurt you?

12:05.550 --> 12:06.390
Tell me,

12:06.990 --> 12:08.520
why did you end up like this?

12:08.600 --> 12:09.600
Tell me the truth!

12:11.000 --> 12:11.790
Senior.

12:12.750 --> 12:14.030
You once asked me,

12:14.870 --> 12:16.910
where my home is in North Xiang.

12:17.790 --> 12:19.030
What I told you then,

12:19.260 --> 12:20.320
that I have no home,

12:20.580 --> 12:22.150
wasn't exactly a lie.

12:24.380 --> 12:26.180
That place is indeed not my home.

12:27.000 --> 12:28.720
He’s not exactly family either.

12:28.720 --> 12:30.120
But I have an enemy.

12:31.440 --> 12:34.200
We share a bitter and deep-seated hatred.

12:36.720 --> 12:37.580
That person...

12:38.240 --> 12:40.270
is my biological father.

12:43.720 --> 12:45.520
Wushui Cliff is extremely tall,

12:45.620 --> 12:47.790
teeming with poisonous mountains
and swarms of insects.

12:47.790 --> 12:48.520
Even if he is

12:48.550 --> 12:50.270
extremely skilled at the Void Stage,

12:50.270 --> 12:51.600
he cannot escape death.

12:57.200 --> 12:57.870
Senior,

12:58.600 --> 12:59.400
rest assured,

12:59.870 --> 13:00.930
he is dead for sure.

13:01.390 --> 13:02.510
Those sons of his

13:02.510 --> 13:03.440
are all dead too.

13:03.840 --> 13:05.840
I even burned down the Qianyan Cave.

13:06.120 --> 13:07.080
In the future, he will never

13:07.080 --> 13:08.880
come to cause you trouble again.

13:12.390 --> 13:13.870
Although he gave me life,

13:14.850 --> 13:16.600
he never treated me as a human.

13:15.390 --> 13:18.700
♪ Hear the Gu curse
turn into cries for help ♪

13:17.150 --> 13:18.270
He originally wanted to

13:18.270 --> 13:19.080
kill me in the womb.

13:18.760 --> 13:22.670
♪ Blood-stained hand, sword drawn ♪

13:19.770 --> 13:21.370
I was lucky to survive.

13:22.700 --> 13:26.170
♪ Trapped in Qianyan Cave ♪

13:23.240 --> 13:24.480
In that Qianyan Cave,

13:25.120 --> 13:27.480
everyone could bully me

13:26.200 --> 13:29.670
♪ Even hell must be broken free from ♪

13:27.480 --> 13:28.150
and beat me.

13:29.080 --> 13:31.030
He didn't teach me any techniques either.

13:30.800 --> 13:33.980
♪ With every stroke of hatred ♪

13:31.870 --> 13:33.600
If it weren't for my tough luck,

13:34.000 --> 13:38.020
♪ Let it grow into a dagger I wear ♪

13:34.150 --> 13:36.280
I would have died at his hands long ago.

13:38.040 --> 13:40.280
♪ No need to show me mercy there ♪

13:40.310 --> 13:44.140
♪ Let me take every blow ♪

13:41.200 --> 13:41.910
Senior.

13:42.600 --> 13:43.630
He is not human.

13:44.150 --> 13:45.840
He is a beast, a sinner!

13:45.760 --> 13:49.860
♪ Drag my wounds through the hollow road ♪

13:46.120 --> 13:47.240
The number of people who died at his hands

13:47.240 --> 13:48.080
is countless.

13:48.360 --> 13:49.420
He deserves to die!

13:49.890 --> 13:53.170
♪ I'll pluck the passion
locked in my brow ♪

13:52.840 --> 13:53.650
Senior,

13:53.190 --> 13:56.560
♪ At the end of the mountains,
I pick up fireflies now ♪

13:54.440 --> 13:55.240
what's wrong?

13:56.580 --> 14:00.730
♪ Burn me down, I feel no pain ♪

13:56.720 --> 13:57.780
Why are you crying?

14:00.770 --> 14:02.360
♪ I believe Heaven sees all ♪

14:01.240 --> 14:01.960
Sheng.

14:02.380 --> 14:04.650
♪ Its wrath shines upon demons ♪

14:03.080 --> 14:03.870
I'm sorry.

14:04.830 --> 14:08.210
♪ But who will show me mercy? ♪

14:05.510 --> 14:06.910
You've suffered so much.

14:07.840 --> 14:08.790
Senior.

14:08.370 --> 14:09.890
♪ I believe I'm innocent ♪

14:09.920 --> 14:14.890
♪ Turned into dust and scattered away ♪

14:10.000 --> 14:11.730
This has nothing to do with you.

14:13.000 --> 14:14.390
I'm sorry, Sheng.

14:15.100 --> 14:18.310
♪ I accept this trial of love
fate has given me ♪

14:18.330 --> 14:22.760
♪ I take in both love and hate alike ♪

14:51.320 --> 14:52.580
She has fallen asleep?

14:54.240 --> 14:55.100
Are you hungry?

14:55.200 --> 14:56.800
Do you want something to eat?

14:57.390 --> 14:59.150
I don't have much of an appetite.

14:59.150 --> 15:00.350
If you're not hungry,

15:00.360 --> 15:02.270
you still need to drink your medicine.

15:02.270 --> 15:03.900
If you can't even take care of yourself,

15:03.900 --> 15:05.960
how will you take care of your junior?

15:07.630 --> 15:08.240
Let's go.

15:14.670 --> 15:15.800
So that's the story.

15:16.200 --> 15:17.080
I was wondering

15:17.670 --> 15:18.220
why those people

15:18.220 --> 15:19.480
would die so suddenly.

15:20.080 --> 15:22.080
So it was all because of your junior.

15:23.080 --> 15:25.360
Xia Xuanzi is an expert of the Void Stage.

15:25.800 --> 15:27.460
and is skilled in the use of Gu.

15:27.630 --> 15:30.490
Even you would have a hard time
winning against her.

15:30.840 --> 15:31.810
Not to mention,

15:32.000 --> 15:34.060
she is just a Golden Core cultivator.

15:37.550 --> 15:38.150
Didn't you see

15:38.150 --> 15:39.550
those wounds on her body?

15:41.300 --> 15:42.330
Your junior

15:42.620 --> 15:43.580
is not someone who easily

15:43.580 --> 15:45.100
opens her heart to others.

15:46.200 --> 15:47.800
Since she treats you this way,

15:47.800 --> 15:48.470
it means

15:48.600 --> 15:50.060
you're really good to her.

15:52.270 --> 15:53.550
You said before

15:53.880 --> 15:55.160
that the disciples of Xin Xie Manor

15:55.160 --> 15:56.430
had all died

15:56.460 --> 15:57.480
in the Battle of Pinghu.

15:57.480 --> 15:58.240
So Sheng

15:58.390 --> 15:59.920
joined Xin Xie Manor later?

16:01.270 --> 16:02.630
That was

16:02.860 --> 16:04.140
many years ago.

16:08.080 --> 16:10.480
I was ordered by my Master to
go to the capital for an errand,

16:10.480 --> 16:11.840
and met Sheng there.

16:12.630 --> 16:14.440
She was having a hard time back then,

16:14.440 --> 16:15.840
and was so thin and small.

16:16.270 --> 16:18.130
She was wandering on the streets.

16:38.030 --> 16:38.600
What?

16:38.790 --> 16:40.390
Can't I even take shelter from the rain?

16:40.390 --> 16:40.910
Here.

16:41.670 --> 16:42.360
That customer just now

16:42.360 --> 16:43.120
bought it for you.

16:43.120 --> 16:44.150
Be careful when you eat.

16:44.150 --> 16:45.280
Don't break my bowl.

16:59.830 --> 17:01.430
I hadn't finished my errand,

17:01.430 --> 17:03.430
so I rented a house and stayed there.

17:05.200 --> 17:06.000
And then...

17:06.880 --> 17:08.030
I met her again.

17:35.000 --> 17:35.680
And then?

17:36.160 --> 17:37.270
Then whenever I had time,

17:37.270 --> 17:38.790
I would often go look for her,

17:38.790 --> 17:40.720
but I couldn't find her most of the time.

17:40.720 --> 17:41.680
She was very shy

17:41.750 --> 17:42.880
and always hid away.

17:43.640 --> 17:44.720
Later I realised

17:45.110 --> 17:46.640
that once I stopped looking for her,

17:46.640 --> 17:48.900
she would always come to see me secretly.

18:06.270 --> 18:06.920
Come here.

18:09.680 --> 18:10.350
Come here.

18:42.440 --> 18:43.070
Eat up.

18:56.110 --> 18:56.910
Did she eat it?

18:57.240 --> 18:58.640
She ate it all up.

18:58.920 --> 19:00.850
After that, she kept coming for me.

19:00.940 --> 19:02.350
She would give me an egg one day,

19:02.350 --> 19:04.350
and some wild vegetables tomorrow.

19:04.960 --> 19:06.580
But she never came close to me,

19:06.580 --> 19:07.650
or talked to me.

19:08.070 --> 19:10.200
This went on for about 2 months,

19:10.830 --> 19:12.640
until something unexpected happened
with my plans,

19:12.640 --> 19:14.240
and I had to leave the capital overnight.

19:14.240 --> 19:15.500
By the time I came back,

19:15.680 --> 19:16.880
it was

19:16.920 --> 19:18.450
more than half a year later.

19:20.480 --> 19:21.680
I went to look for her.

19:21.680 --> 19:22.880
I searched for 3 days.

19:23.040 --> 19:24.440
Finally, on the last day,

19:24.790 --> 19:25.720
I found her.

19:28.350 --> 19:29.110
Brat!

19:29.380 --> 19:30.420
Let's teach her a lesson.

19:30.420 --> 19:31.080
Beat her up!

19:38.750 --> 19:39.720
Still not leaving?

19:39.720 --> 19:41.050
Go, go!

19:42.840 --> 19:43.610
Are you okay?

19:43.960 --> 19:45.160
Why did they beat you?

19:46.510 --> 19:47.620
Don't cry.

19:48.960 --> 19:49.550
Did they

19:49.550 --> 19:50.680
hurt you somewhere?

19:51.550 --> 19:52.410
All's fine now.

19:53.050 --> 19:54.220
It's okay.

19:59.790 --> 20:00.480
And then?

20:01.560 --> 20:03.400
And then I brought her back.

20:03.960 --> 20:06.020
Xin Xie Manor is sparsely populated.

20:06.240 --> 20:07.770
It was just me and my Master.

20:07.840 --> 20:08.970
After Sheng came,

20:09.000 --> 20:10.400
it became a lot livelier.

20:10.790 --> 20:11.990
And she has immortal perception

20:11.990 --> 20:12.990
and great talent.

20:13.160 --> 20:14.960
She cultivates faster than I do.

20:18.780 --> 20:19.610
Maybe it's because

20:19.610 --> 20:21.270
I was the one who brought her back,

20:21.270 --> 20:22.480
so she relies on me a lot

20:22.480 --> 20:24.280
and listens to everything I say.

20:24.510 --> 20:25.840
I have to thank her, too.

20:26.110 --> 20:27.310
If it weren't for her,

20:27.470 --> 20:28.390
I wouldn't know

20:28.560 --> 20:29.110
how I would have survived

20:29.110 --> 20:30.200
all these years.

20:30.240 --> 20:31.720
You seem to really like your junior.

20:31.720 --> 20:32.470
Of course.

20:33.250 --> 20:34.420
She's my family.

20:55.760 --> 20:57.170
[Phoenix City]

21:03.160 --> 21:03.960
Knock on the door.

21:03.960 --> 21:04.550
Yes.

21:24.680 --> 21:26.000
With such terrible handwriting,

21:26.000 --> 21:27.680
how do you have the nerve to show it?

21:27.680 --> 21:28.510
I want to.

21:28.720 --> 21:29.590
None of your business.

21:29.590 --> 21:30.960
Do you know what it means?

21:30.960 --> 21:31.790
I know.

21:32.240 --> 21:34.440
Brother Tang had taught me everything.

21:35.110 --> 21:36.510
What, changed your mind?

21:36.560 --> 21:37.340
Don't want to learn swordsmanship

21:37.340 --> 21:38.870
from Brother Rust-Sword anymore?

21:38.870 --> 21:39.910
Of course I do.

21:40.070 --> 21:41.520
Then you'd better think it through.

21:41.520 --> 21:42.430
If you consider

21:42.460 --> 21:44.240
my Brother Rust-Sword as your master,

21:44.240 --> 21:46.440
you'll have to call me Uncle from now on.

21:48.180 --> 21:49.040
In your dreams!

21:49.110 --> 21:50.710
I can't be bothered with you.

22:00.790 --> 22:01.400
Master,

22:01.770 --> 22:02.570
have some tea.

22:16.830 --> 22:18.110
What are you playing at?

22:18.110 --> 22:19.510
I know you're not asleep.

22:22.840 --> 22:23.600
Sister Zhanying.

22:23.600 --> 22:25.530
Don't keep calling me your sister.

22:25.640 --> 22:26.900
I'm not older than you.

22:28.790 --> 22:29.920
Take off your boots.

22:32.280 --> 22:33.470
Your boots are torn.

22:33.590 --> 22:35.200
Come here, let me sew them up for you.

22:35.200 --> 22:35.880
Torn?

22:41.510 --> 22:43.640
That's not very appropriate, Sister.

22:52.270 --> 22:54.470
You actually know how to do needlework?

22:54.960 --> 22:55.640
Of course.

22:55.970 --> 22:57.180
Who wasn't a delicate young lady

22:57.180 --> 22:58.270
in her youth?

22:58.940 --> 22:59.980
Embroidery, repairs,

22:59.980 --> 23:00.930
I learned it all.

23:01.750 --> 23:02.400
If my family hadn't suffered

23:02.400 --> 23:03.750
a misfortune afterwards,

23:03.750 --> 23:05.030
and I hadn't learned martial arts,

23:05.030 --> 23:05.720
I might have become

23:05.720 --> 23:07.180
a top-notch embroiderer.

23:17.110 --> 23:17.750
Try it on.

23:19.210 --> 23:20.270
You're quite good.

23:23.790 --> 23:24.350
How is it?

23:27.430 --> 23:28.300
It'll do.

23:32.000 --> 23:32.900
After Tai Shiqian and the others

23:32.900 --> 23:34.360
finish copying the books,

23:34.440 --> 23:35.700
where do you plan to go?

23:36.110 --> 23:36.440
I—

23:36.440 --> 23:37.840
If you have nowhere to go,

23:37.890 --> 23:40.090
why not come back to my hometown with me?

23:40.760 --> 23:42.250
You have plenty of strength.

23:42.250 --> 23:43.000
When the time comes,

23:43.000 --> 23:44.680
you'll farm while I'll weave cloth.

23:44.680 --> 23:45.680
Together,

23:45.720 --> 23:47.480
we can definitely live a good life.

23:47.480 --> 23:48.480
I'd better not.

23:49.030 --> 23:50.160
I’ve had a rough life.

23:50.160 --> 23:52.220
I simply don't have what it takes
to enjoy marriage.

23:52.220 --> 23:52.800
I want to become

23:52.800 --> 23:54.290
the best swordsman in the world.

23:54.290 --> 23:54.910
For the rest of my life,

23:54.910 --> 23:55.930
I am destined to wander on the road,

23:55.930 --> 23:57.260
spending a lonely life.

23:57.480 --> 23:58.480
Sister Zhanying,

23:58.720 --> 24:00.510
you should find someone else to fancy.

24:00.510 --> 24:01.310
Someone else?

24:02.290 --> 24:03.660
But among all these people,

24:03.660 --> 24:05.120
I have fallen for only you.

24:05.550 --> 24:06.210
Others...

24:08.400 --> 24:09.000
Forget it.

24:09.740 --> 24:11.600
You don't need to worry too much about it.

24:11.600 --> 24:12.830
I might like you today,

24:12.830 --> 24:13.810
but maybe tomorrow,

24:13.810 --> 24:15.140
I won't like you anymore

24:15.270 --> 24:17.130
once I meet a better-looking man.

24:18.750 --> 24:20.410
That would be a true blessing.

24:21.660 --> 24:22.600
We only have a few days

24:22.600 --> 24:23.530
left together,

24:24.110 --> 24:25.510
so you should cherish me.

24:29.920 --> 24:31.180
What day is it already?

24:33.470 --> 24:34.400
It's been 8 days.

24:35.780 --> 24:36.710
It's been 8 days?

24:39.110 --> 24:40.040
It won't be long.

24:42.350 --> 24:43.030
Yeah.

24:44.200 --> 24:45.130
It won't be long.

24:58.200 --> 25:00.380
The plows of Qin, the rakes of Chu,
the sickles of Yan,

25:00.380 --> 25:01.160
the hoes of Zhao and Wei,

25:01.160 --> 25:03.200
though they may till the same soil,
they are not fit for the task,

25:03.200 --> 25:04.490
because the nature of
the soil is different.

25:04.490 --> 25:06.310
The plows of Qin, the rakes of Chu,
the sickles of Yan,

25:06.310 --> 25:07.790
the hoes of Zhao and Wei—

25:08.550 --> 25:09.750
Can you recite silently?

25:09.750 --> 25:11.430
You made me memorize it all wrong.

25:11.430 --> 25:12.140
I can't.

25:12.270 --> 25:13.470
If I don't read aloud,

25:13.550 --> 25:14.680
I can't memorize it.

25:15.000 --> 25:16.200
What should I do then?

25:17.790 --> 25:19.520
I'll go memorize it over there.

25:38.720 --> 25:40.120
Anyway, that's how it is.

25:40.940 --> 25:42.170
Regardless of what could be shared,

25:42.170 --> 25:43.350
I’ve said everything there is to say.

25:43.350 --> 25:44.550
What else do you want?

25:44.640 --> 25:46.240
Junior Lin, you're worrying too much.

25:46.240 --> 25:47.590
We just can't figure out,

25:47.590 --> 25:49.830
if Lu Qianqiao had taken you as a hostage,

25:49.830 --> 25:51.160
why would he suddenly let you go?

25:51.160 --> 25:52.240
According to you,

25:52.640 --> 25:54.270
I deserved to be killed by him,

25:54.270 --> 25:56.530
and only then it would make sense, right?

25:59.070 --> 26:00.530
Senior Bai is just asking.

26:00.830 --> 26:02.510
Why get so worked up over it?

26:02.830 --> 26:03.630
Junior Jiang,

26:04.510 --> 26:05.590
what kind of magic potion

26:05.590 --> 26:06.960
did this guy surnamed Bai feed you?

26:06.960 --> 26:07.760
Don't forget,

26:08.000 --> 26:09.590
we are from the same sect.

26:10.750 --> 26:11.510
Senior Lin,

26:11.920 --> 26:12.880
calm down.

26:13.750 --> 26:15.510
Those demonic cultivators
are cunning

26:15.510 --> 26:17.040
and difficult to deal with.

26:17.750 --> 26:19.200
We just feel it's a shame

26:19.780 --> 26:20.970
they got away again.

26:21.640 --> 26:22.640
Logically speaking,

26:22.640 --> 26:24.830
with your brilliance and martial prowess,

26:24.830 --> 26:26.550
this shouldn't have happened.

26:26.550 --> 26:27.410
Could there...

26:27.640 --> 26:29.480
be more to the story?

26:31.880 --> 26:33.830
Only you would be so sarcastic.

26:34.410 --> 26:35.940
If you want to scold me, be direct.

26:35.940 --> 26:37.470
Don't beat around the bush.

26:39.310 --> 26:40.240
I wouldn't dare.

26:40.560 --> 26:41.810
Of course you wouldn't dare.

26:41.810 --> 26:43.270
You have no rights either.

26:44.640 --> 26:45.720
He's at least

26:45.790 --> 26:48.050
a Heavenly Talent born on
September 9th.

26:48.070 --> 26:49.790
I’d put up with a few words of
his criticism.

26:49.790 --> 26:51.110
Who do you think you are,

26:51.110 --> 26:52.270
going on and on about me?

26:52.270 --> 26:53.600
What about Lu Qianqiao?

26:56.000 --> 26:56.960
Is he still with those

26:56.960 --> 26:58.360
demonized cultivators?

27:00.830 --> 27:01.560
I don't know.

27:02.070 --> 27:03.130
Why don't you know?

27:03.550 --> 27:04.270
Didn't you leave

27:04.270 --> 27:05.000
with them?

27:06.710 --> 27:07.580
That day,

27:07.920 --> 27:08.920
we got separated.

27:10.240 --> 27:11.640
We have been observing them

27:11.640 --> 27:12.550
these few days.

27:12.920 --> 27:14.440
After entering Sihe Library,

27:14.440 --> 27:15.680
they haven't come out since.

27:15.680 --> 27:16.750
And I haven't seen

27:16.750 --> 27:17.950
that guy surnamed Lu.

27:18.200 --> 27:19.660
I don't know where he went.

27:19.790 --> 27:20.880
Intercepting them on the road

27:20.880 --> 27:22.680
was originally the best choice.

27:22.750 --> 27:23.880
Now that they are in the library,

27:23.880 --> 27:24.940
it's not as simple.

27:25.440 --> 27:26.480
This Sihe Library

27:26.830 --> 27:28.750
has a heritage of a thousand years.

27:28.750 --> 27:29.920
It has always been
a sanctuary for scholars

27:29.920 --> 27:31.050
seeking knowledge.

27:31.440 --> 27:32.400
There are many scholars

27:32.400 --> 27:33.260
here right now.

27:33.440 --> 27:34.510
If we act rashly,

27:35.480 --> 27:37.680
I'm afraid the innocent will be harmed.

27:37.680 --> 27:39.400
We have too little information.

27:39.400 --> 27:40.930
How many enemies are there?

27:41.030 --> 27:42.350
Do they have any backup?

27:42.350 --> 27:43.610
The slightest mistake

27:43.960 --> 27:45.290
can lead to oversights.

27:45.830 --> 27:47.890
Then let's just burn everything down

27:48.400 --> 27:49.790
and end it once and for all.

27:49.790 --> 27:50.720
What did you say?

27:51.830 --> 27:52.720
Otherwise, do you have a

27:52.720 --> 27:53.830
better idea?

27:55.070 --> 27:56.930
They are all demons and heretics.

27:56.960 --> 27:58.160
They deserve to die.

27:58.590 --> 27:59.200
I heard

27:59.240 --> 28:00.270
that Sihe Library

28:00.270 --> 28:01.930
opens only once every 5 years.

28:02.110 --> 28:03.000
Even if we

28:03.000 --> 28:04.130
kill them all today,

28:04.790 --> 28:06.720
as long as Sihe Library exists,

28:07.240 --> 28:08.160
5 years later,

28:08.640 --> 28:09.920
they will definitely send

28:09.920 --> 28:11.120
a new batch of people.

28:11.790 --> 28:12.680
Are we going to

28:12.830 --> 28:14.510
capture them again then?

28:14.830 --> 28:16.400
Junior Jiang makes sense.

28:17.000 --> 28:18.600
Destroying just one library

28:18.650 --> 28:21.250
can destroy the demons'
hopes for resurrection.

28:21.250 --> 28:22.260
It's totally worth it.

28:22.260 --> 28:23.920
We can't destroy it so easily.

28:24.220 --> 28:27.060
There are way too many classics
in Sihe Library.

28:27.550 --> 28:28.110
Senior,

28:28.350 --> 28:29.090
have you forgotten

28:29.090 --> 28:30.290
how many humans and

28:30.680 --> 28:32.110
how many immortals died during

28:32.110 --> 28:33.970
the God-Demon War many years ago?

28:34.270 --> 28:35.590
At that time,
the heavenly ladder was intact,

28:35.590 --> 28:36.640
and the deities could still help us

28:36.640 --> 28:37.640
fight against the demons.

28:37.640 --> 28:38.840
Even with their help,

28:38.880 --> 28:40.350
we still suffered great casualties,

28:40.350 --> 28:41.830
and corpses littered the ground.

28:41.830 --> 28:43.240
Now that the deities are gone,

28:43.240 --> 28:44.440
if the demons revive,

28:45.070 --> 28:46.270
who will resist them?

28:50.510 --> 28:51.680
This Sihe Library

28:51.750 --> 28:53.160
collects books from all over the world,

28:53.160 --> 28:55.070
and its original intention was good.

28:55.070 --> 28:55.640
But

28:56.110 --> 28:58.070
the fact that the demonic manuals
were mixed in,

28:58.070 --> 28:59.400
that itself is a sin.

29:00.030 --> 29:00.590
Senior,

29:00.880 --> 29:02.680
don’t think I’m being heartless,

29:02.680 --> 29:04.210
but I still have to say this.

29:04.400 --> 29:06.530
So what if we destroy just one library?

29:06.700 --> 29:08.150
Even if I bleed out

29:08.240 --> 29:09.170
and lose my life,

29:09.310 --> 29:10.570
I am more than willing.

29:15.920 --> 29:16.510
Senior,

29:16.830 --> 29:18.350
I'm willing to lead the way.

29:18.350 --> 29:20.170
Even if it means being condemned
for all eternity,

29:20.170 --> 29:21.200
I will eradicate the demons

29:21.200 --> 29:21.930
for the world

29:22.030 --> 29:23.240
and the immortal sect.

29:23.240 --> 29:25.750
Please let me enter Sihe Library, Senior.

29:32.960 --> 29:33.720
Remember.

29:34.830 --> 29:36.030
Your primary mission

29:36.440 --> 29:37.960
is to destroy the
"Unparalleled Secret Magic".

29:37.960 --> 29:39.690
Unless absolutely necessary,

29:40.240 --> 29:42.100
you must not destroy the library.

29:42.590 --> 29:43.720
Don't worry, Senior.

29:43.720 --> 29:44.750
I am not crazy.

29:45.200 --> 29:45.960
Besides,

29:46.550 --> 29:48.000
those demonic cultivators

29:48.000 --> 29:48.440
are just a bunch of

29:48.440 --> 29:50.160
defenseless bookworms.

29:50.550 --> 29:52.200
Taking two juniors with me would suffice.

29:52.200 --> 29:53.270
Their main forces

29:53.550 --> 29:56.410
will definitely be
defending outside the library.

29:56.590 --> 29:58.790
When the time comes, please join forces

29:59.070 --> 30:00.670
to fight this powerful enemy

30:00.830 --> 30:02.070
and buy me some time.

30:02.440 --> 30:03.240
Rest assured.

30:03.830 --> 30:05.490
With my Chengying Sword here,

30:07.200 --> 30:07.920
they certainly

30:07.920 --> 30:09.920
won't be able to stir up any trouble.

30:31.350 --> 30:31.960
Jin Lun?

30:33.830 --> 30:34.550
Jin Lun?

31:23.790 --> 31:24.590
Let go of me.

31:26.920 --> 31:27.850
Let go of me!

31:31.090 --> 31:31.830
Let go of me.

31:32.350 --> 31:33.010
Let go of me.

31:36.920 --> 31:37.790
Let go of me!

31:42.110 --> 31:42.720
Sheng?

31:42.870 --> 31:43.750
Sheng, what's wrong with you?

31:43.750 --> 31:44.400
Let go of me!

31:44.400 --> 31:45.260
Sheng, wake up.

31:46.510 --> 31:47.200
Let go of me.

31:48.240 --> 31:48.900
Let go of me.

31:49.270 --> 31:50.030
Let go of me!

31:50.240 --> 31:50.960
Let go of me.

31:52.750 --> 31:53.240
Sheng!

31:53.470 --> 31:54.400
Sheng, wake up!

31:54.590 --> 31:55.070
Sheng!

31:56.200 --> 31:57.400
Sheng, what's wrong?

31:57.440 --> 31:58.900
Sheng, don't be like this!

31:59.290 --> 32:00.090
Sheng.

32:00.590 --> 32:01.440
Sheng, wake up.

32:01.440 --> 32:01.790
Let me go!

32:01.790 --> 32:02.350
Sheng!

32:02.420 --> 32:03.920
Let me go!

32:04.070 --> 32:05.070
What's wrong with her?

32:05.070 --> 32:05.800
I don't know.

32:05.830 --> 32:07.160
I just can't wake her up.

32:08.270 --> 32:08.830
No!

32:08.960 --> 32:09.550
No!

32:28.830 --> 32:30.590
Sheng, you're awake.

32:31.330 --> 32:32.200
Senior.

32:32.470 --> 32:33.270
What's wrong?

32:41.270 --> 32:42.000
Senior.

32:42.420 --> 32:44.030
Let's go back to Xin Xie Manor.

32:44.030 --> 32:44.960
I want to go home.

32:47.960 --> 32:49.940
The fish we raised in the pond last year

32:49.940 --> 32:51.200
should be plump by now.

32:52.110 --> 32:53.910
I want to eat your grilled fish.

32:55.160 --> 32:57.160
Let's go back to Xin Xie Manor, okay?

32:57.370 --> 32:58.370
I hate it here.

32:58.590 --> 32:59.650
I hate North Xiang.

33:01.270 --> 33:02.880
Once you recover from your injuries,

33:02.880 --> 33:04.410
we will leave immediately.

33:19.180 --> 33:20.660
The main dish is here!

33:25.480 --> 33:28.010
I specifically warmed up
a pot of wine for you.

33:28.550 --> 33:29.950
Thanks for the hard work.

33:30.110 --> 33:31.280
Sha deserves some credit too.

33:31.280 --> 33:32.590
I didn't really help muxg.

33:32.590 --> 33:33.990
I just assisted a little.

33:36.240 --> 33:38.210
Miss Sheng, you just recovered
from a serious illness,

33:38.210 --> 33:39.160
so you should eat more.

33:39.160 --> 33:40.920
I killed this fish.

33:41.200 --> 33:41.830
Try it.

33:46.490 --> 33:47.670
Senior, you have it.

33:49.900 --> 33:51.230
You should eat more too.

33:51.880 --> 33:52.940
Thank you, Senior.

33:54.480 --> 33:55.640
Let's all eat!

33:56.390 --> 33:57.790
Here, let me pour for you.

34:06.750 --> 34:07.880
What kind of wine is this?

34:07.880 --> 34:08.960
It smells so good.

34:12.550 --> 34:13.880
If you want to drink it,

34:14.280 --> 34:15.480
why don't you have it?

34:23.760 --> 34:25.030
L-Lu, I'm sorry.

34:25.630 --> 34:27.070
My stool...

34:27.489 --> 34:28.360
The wine spilled.

34:28.360 --> 34:30.290
I'll go warm up another pot for you.

34:45.070 --> 34:45.840
I know what

34:45.840 --> 34:46.570
you are up to.

34:49.300 --> 34:51.159
You're trying to trick my senior.

34:51.350 --> 34:52.210
Let me tell you.

34:52.280 --> 34:53.139
With me around,

34:53.250 --> 34:54.610
don't even think about it.

34:54.610 --> 34:56.610
You know my senior is kind-hearted,

34:56.639 --> 34:58.110
so you deliberately acted weak

34:58.110 --> 34:59.910
and pretended to be wronged,

35:00.190 --> 35:02.390
in order to trick her into marrying you.

35:02.600 --> 35:03.860
After your scheme was exposed,

35:03.860 --> 35:05.290
you erased her memory.

35:05.800 --> 35:07.130
You feigned closeness,

35:07.230 --> 35:08.670
repeated your trick,

35:08.960 --> 35:10.150
and did it again.

35:10.630 --> 35:12.220
You must be overjoyed now,

35:12.510 --> 35:14.440
thinking your plan had succeeded.

35:14.550 --> 35:16.710
You're the one pretending
to be weak and pitiful,

35:16.710 --> 35:18.910
all while scheming tricks, aren't you?

35:19.670 --> 35:20.600
What did you say?

35:22.070 --> 35:23.730
As the daughter of Xia Xuanzi,

35:23.960 --> 35:25.070
you could walk out alive

35:25.070 --> 35:27.000
from a place like the Qianyan Cave,

35:27.160 --> 35:28.850
cross the desert alone,

35:28.880 --> 35:30.030
and arrive in the capital.

35:30.030 --> 35:31.110
How could such a person

35:31.110 --> 35:31.800
possibly be beaten up

35:31.800 --> 35:33.150
by a few little beggars

35:33.550 --> 35:35.440
without being able to fight back?

35:36.320 --> 35:37.070
Little girl,

35:37.760 --> 35:38.880
in front of me,

35:39.430 --> 35:41.430
just stop doing all these nonsense.

36:03.920 --> 36:04.850
This looks good.

36:07.510 --> 36:08.070
Sheng.

36:09.320 --> 36:09.920
Sheng?

36:12.250 --> 36:13.250
Change into this.

36:13.550 --> 36:14.610
Do you find it nice?

36:17.630 --> 36:18.710
If you don't like it,

36:18.710 --> 36:19.840
we can go to the city

36:19.930 --> 36:21.190
and pick what you like.

36:21.800 --> 36:22.510
Senior,

36:23.150 --> 36:24.550
aren't we going home yet?

36:25.840 --> 36:27.900
Wait until your injuries are better.

36:27.960 --> 36:29.030
But I miss home.

36:29.350 --> 36:30.300
Let's go home.

36:30.840 --> 36:31.510
Previously, you said

36:31.510 --> 36:33.290
you wanted to settle scores
with Lu Qianqiao.

36:33.290 --> 36:34.960
Now that the misunderstanding is cleared,

36:34.960 --> 36:36.040
we should go back.

36:37.110 --> 36:39.110
Master is still waiting at the manor.

36:39.110 --> 36:41.040
We can heal my injuries at home too.

36:42.890 --> 36:43.810
But...

36:49.630 --> 36:51.230
And I don't like North Xiang.

36:52.070 --> 36:52.880
I'm scared.

36:54.320 --> 36:56.480
I have nightmares every night,

36:57.070 --> 36:59.130
dreaming that I haven't escaped yet.

36:59.440 --> 37:01.170
That I am still in Qianyan Cave,

37:01.400 --> 37:03.400
tortured by that lunatic every day.

37:04.880 --> 37:06.110
Senior,

37:07.130 --> 37:08.290
I'm so scared.

37:09.590 --> 37:10.850
Let's leave, shall we?

37:13.510 --> 37:14.590
I'm sorry, Sheng.

37:15.480 --> 37:16.630
I was careless.

37:17.350 --> 37:19.210
I didn't consider your feelings.

37:20.480 --> 37:21.110
Let's go.

37:22.230 --> 37:23.490
We'll leave right now.

37:34.770 --> 37:36.440
[Sihe Library]

37:46.480 --> 37:48.150
Hey there! Refill my water!

37:49.070 --> 37:49.840
Coming!

38:14.880 --> 38:15.760
Why does this tea

38:15.760 --> 38:16.920
have no taste at all?

38:17.670 --> 38:18.730
Is it about the tea?

38:19.110 --> 38:20.760
Even if it were the finest tea
in the heavens,

38:20.760 --> 38:21.960
after 8 pots of water,

38:22.150 --> 38:23.280
of course it has no taste.

38:23.280 --> 38:24.960
Then can't you change the tea?

38:25.230 --> 38:25.880
I can.

38:26.880 --> 38:27.940
Will you pay for it?

38:29.670 --> 38:31.150
I booked the whole place.

38:31.590 --> 38:32.670
The whole place!

38:32.920 --> 38:33.880
I already paid!

38:34.190 --> 38:35.150
Booking the place

38:35.150 --> 38:36.350
doesn't include tea.

38:37.920 --> 38:39.120
Do you still want tea?

38:49.000 --> 38:50.110
Drinking water is fine.

38:50.110 --> 38:51.240
It quenches thirst.

38:52.280 --> 38:53.000
Fine.

38:57.550 --> 38:59.360
These are all specialties of North Xiang.

38:59.360 --> 39:01.120
You can't buy them in the Central Plains.

39:01.120 --> 39:02.290
Our Master will definitely

39:02.290 --> 39:03.820
like them when he sees them.

39:05.070 --> 39:06.920
When did you join Xin Xie Manor?

39:07.960 --> 39:09.630
Aren't we all family?

39:10.920 --> 39:11.920
Family?

39:14.840 --> 39:17.000
You and Immortal Xin are family.

39:17.510 --> 39:19.670
Lu and I are family.

39:19.880 --> 39:20.670
Well...

39:23.670 --> 39:25.330
Did I leave something behind?

39:25.710 --> 39:26.770
I'll go count them.

39:27.280 --> 39:29.070
I haven't been to
the Central Plains for years.

39:29.070 --> 39:30.190
I must be fully prepared,

39:30.190 --> 39:31.590
seeing you off this time.

39:36.800 --> 39:37.590
I'm sorry.

39:38.230 --> 39:40.070
I promised to stay with you,

39:40.920 --> 39:42.150
but Sheng...

39:43.380 --> 39:44.250
It's fine.

39:44.670 --> 39:46.870
It's not like we won't
see each other again.

39:46.870 --> 39:48.320
Once I finish my work here,

39:48.320 --> 39:49.320
I will go find you.

39:49.960 --> 39:50.710
Really?

39:50.920 --> 39:51.590
Of course.

39:56.230 --> 39:57.800
While I'm away,

39:58.690 --> 40:00.690
you must take good care of yourself.

40:03.480 --> 40:04.410
Drink less wine.

40:05.670 --> 40:06.320
Okay.

40:08.070 --> 40:10.030
Also, if you have time,

40:10.360 --> 40:11.620
use Spirit Projection

40:12.110 --> 40:13.760
and tell me how you're doing.

40:14.710 --> 40:15.480
I got it.

40:33.780 --> 40:34.570
Senior!

40:37.840 --> 40:38.510
Let's go.

40:38.800 --> 40:39.630
It's time.

40:47.480 --> 40:48.480
I'm leaving then.

40:49.440 --> 40:50.070
Go ahead.
